public class Solution {
    public int reverseBits(int n) {
        int res = 0;
        for(int i = 0; i < 32; i++){
            res = (res << 1) | (n & 1);
            n = n >>> 1;
        }
        return res;
    }
}

Time Complexity: O(1)
The loop runs 32 times (fixed), so itâ€™s constant time.

Space Complexity: O(1)
Uses only a few variables; no extra space grows with input.
